reviewText: I have sentimental ties to that movie because I was extra and actual resident of the trailer park while they were filming it
Not the greatest movie I've ever seen but bought it because I'm a huge fan of Webb Wilder who is in this movie and also has a song in the ending titles which is awesome.

Watching this movie, you can believe that you are standing in the middle of a trailer park. It has the drama and cheese that you can imagine. If you want to see a melodramatic portrayal of the interpersonal dynamics of a WV trailer park, this movie is definitely for you!!
